title: West Bucktown Logan Square( armitage / california) 3 Bedroom 1 Bath
posting_body: ['Available July 1, 2022 in this amazing location, 3 bedroom or 2 bed w/office, 1 bath, raised first floor apartment in a 2 unit building.', 'This light-filled unit has a spacious living area with high ceilings throughout, recessed lighting, hardwood floors, central heat and air conditioning, and side yard.', 'Nice sized closets with a walk-in closet in the largest bedroom.', 'This unit is walking distance(4-6 minutes) to the California "L" blue line stop at milwaukee and california, and all that this great area has to offer near california, armitage and milwaukee.', 'Tenant pays gas and electric.', 'Credit check, and move-in fee required.', 'Pets may be allowed.', 'Please email for a showing.']
